author: Elizabeth Gould
title: Elizabeth Gould
text: Laurie was very helpful and informative. She let me know that it gets windy at her location so I might want to wrap my nicer things in plastic to keep the dirt off. I appreciated that since I just bought my couch. She was very helpful to me. Keep up the good work Laurie.
